"data:image/svg+xml;utf8, "&EncodeUrl("
    
    <svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='10' height='10' fill='" & 
    
    If(
        ThisItem.name = 'menu component'.curentScreen,
        'menu component'.iconColorCurrent,
        'menu component'.iconColor
    )

    & "' viewBox='0 0 16 16'>

    " & ThisItem.path & "

    </svg>

")
